          <div class="tst-author">
            <div class="tst-av">KM</div>
            <div><span class="tst-name">Kavya Menon</span><span class="tst-co">Head of Product · Groww</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tst-card reveal rd1">
          <div class="tst-metric">₹4L saved / quarter</div>
          <p class="tst-quote">"We replaced three separate tools with this one. The ROI was visible in the first month. The setup took a single afternoon — our previous tool took three weeks."</p>
          <div class="tst-author">
            <div class="tst-av">RS</div>
            <div><span class="tst-name">Rohan Suri</span><span class="tst-co">CTO · Series B Startup</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="tst-card reveal rd2">
          <div class="tst-metric">3× team velocity</div>
          <p class="tst-quote">"Every founder told me tooling doesn't matter — just ship. They were wrong. The right tool is a multiplier, and this is the best one we've found for our stage."</p>
          <div class="tst-author">
